### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Create a Badge (replace X-API-Key with seeded value)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/badges
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "name": "Node.js Mastery",
  "description": "Awarded for mastering Node.js fundamentals and advanced concepts.",
  "imageUrl": "https://placehold.co/400x400/22c55e/white?text=Node.js",
  "criteria": "Complete all modules and pass the final exam.",
  "externalCourseId": "111222"
}

###

### Issue Assertion (generic endpoint — replace badgeClassId and X-API-Key)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assertions
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "badgeClassId": "{{BADGE_CLASS_ID}}",
  "recipientEmail": "test@example.com",
  "recipientName": "Test User"
}

###

### Course Completed Webhook (replace X-API-Key with seeded value)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/webhooks/course-completed
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "resource": "course",
  "action": "completed",
  "payload": {
    "user": {
      "email": "mario.rossi@example.com",
      "first_name": "Mario",
      "last_name": "Rossi"
    },
    "course": {
      "id": 987654,
      "name": "Corso React Advanced"
    }
  }
}

###

### Verify Badge (HTML page — replace assertionId)
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/{{ASSERTION_ID}}

###

### Get Raw Credential (JSON-LD — replace assertionId)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assertions/{{ASSERTION_ID}}

###

### Get Tenant Public Key (replace tenantId)
GET http://localhost:3000/keys/{{TENANT_ID}}
